## 🛠️ 开发

### 从源码安装

```bash
# 克隆仓库
git clone https://github.com/punitarani/fli.git
cd fli

# 使用 Poetry 安装依赖
poetry install

# 运行测试
poetry run pytest

# 运行代码检查
poetry run ruff check .
poetry run ruff format .

# 构建文档
poetry run mkdocs serve
```

### 构建和发布

```bash
# 构建包
poetry build

# 发布到 PyPI
poetry publish
```

